name: Lakeside Apartment in Tata
description:
Our apartment is located in the peaceful environment of the Old Lake, with a beautiful view to the Castle.

The lakeside promenade is just outside the door, the city center is 5-10 min. walk. Fully equipped kitchen, two bedrooms with double bed and convertible sofa in the living room.

Tata has connection to main highways, you can reach for example Budapest and Győr (Audi factory) in ca 30 minutes, Vienna in ca 1,5 hour and Bratislava in ca 1 hour on the highway. Komarno/Komarom (Foxconn, Nokia, Mylan) is about 30 minutes drive, Tatabánya Development Zone (Samsung, Bridgestone, AGC, Coloplast, Eural, FCI, SANMINA-SCI) is a 10 minutes drive on the road no. 1.

The apartment is located in one of the best spots in Tata, inside a natural reserve area. It has a beautiful panorama to the lake, the castle and other highlights of Tata, it's a perfect starting point for walks in the city or around the Lake. In a 5-10 minutes walking distance you can find restaurants, bars, supermarkets, confectionary, bank, post office, and also a huge, beautiful park.

There are many possibilites for doing sports in the city, open-air and closed swimming pools, golf course, fitness clubs are all close to the aparment.

The house has two stories, the aparment is located downstairs with separate entrance. The apartment has two bedrooms, both with double beds, and a convertible sofa in the living room, so it can host up to 5-6 people.

In the kitchen you can use the refrigator, microvawe, dish-washer, electric kettle, toaster. There is also a shared washing machine, which is outside the aparment. You can access it through the inner yard anytime in a separate room.

Parking is for free in the area, there are available parking places in front of the house. Two bikes are also available, one is equipped with child seat.

You can get in touch with with us via phone or e-mail any time, or just ring the doorbell when we are home, because we are living upstairs. We can help you if you have any questions about the city - highlights, shopping options, directions, etc., so don't hesitate to contact us!
You can also use Wi-Fi in the whole apartment.

This aparment is also available for long term rent, in this case please conact us for individual price!
